node.text: A painting I did recently for a potential art concept my band @go_band_tpa was going to use as a single cover. Depicting the feeling I had at times during March April and May of 2020. We decided not to use it so I’m sharing it here. It’s titled “Have We Become the Ghosts” done only acrylic on canvas. #paintings #artallthetime #artoftheday #paintingconcepts #socialdistance #ghosts #gobandtpa
